quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,“Ndikulumbilira usiku pamene ukuphimba (chilichonse)
  92,2,“Ndi usana pamene kukuyera
  92,3,“Ndiponso Yemwe adalenga chachimuna ndi chachikazi
  92,4,“Ndithu zochita zanu nzosiyanasiyana
  92,5,“Tsono yemwe akupereka (pa njira ya Allah) ndikumamuopa (Mbuye wake ndikupewa zoletsedwa)
  92,6,“Ndikumavomereza zinthu zabwino; (komwe kuli kukhulupirira Allah mwanzeru)
  92,7,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku zabwino
  92,8,“Koma uyo achite umbombo ndikuganiza za kuti iye payekha ngokwana
  92,9,“Ndi kumatsutsa zinthu zabwino
  92,10,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku mavuto (a muyaya)
  92,11,“Ndipo chuma chake sichidzamthandiza (chilichonse) akadzagwera ku Moto
  92,12,“Ndithu Ife ndi amene timawalongosolera anthu njira yabwino ndi njira yoipa
  92,13,“Ndipo ndithu moyo womaliza ndi moyo woyamba uli m’manja mwathu
  92,14,"“Basi, ndikukuchenjezani za Moto woyaka mwa mphamvu"
  92,15,“Sakaulowa koma (kafiri) woipitsitsa kwambiri
  92,16,“Yemwe amatsutsa (choona) ndi kunyoza (zisonyezo za Allah)
  92,17,“Koma yemwe akuopa Allah kwambiri akatalikitsidwa ndi Moto
  92,18,“Amene akupereka chuma chake ndi cholinga chodziyeretsa
  92,19,"“Ndipo palibe aliyense kwa iye, amene adamchitira za chifundo zomwe zikulipidwa"
  92,20,“Koma (akuchita zimenezi) kufuna chikondi cha Mbuye wake Wapamwambamwamba
  92,21,“Ndipo posachedwa adzasangalala